surveys_hindfoot_half <- surveys %>%
  filter(!is.na(hindfoot_length)) %>% 
  mutate(hindfoot_half = hindfoot_length /2) %>% 
  filter(hindfoot_half < 30) %>% 
  select(species_id, hindfoot_half)
